    "discriminators": [
     "The covering, not the window: fabric swish and slat rattle. Very bright, very quiet, almost no low_band_energy, high spectral_flatness — a soft noise texture with no structural thud anywhere.",
     "That absence of a heavy low-frequency frame impact is the whole separation from WNDWWood / WNDWMetl / WNDWPlas, which all end in a sash thump.",
     "Venetian slats add a dense clattering transient train; a curtain drag is pure friction. Both stay light and high-centroid."
    ],
