    "discriminators": [
     "Small bright metal fittings — latch, crank, catch. Spiky, high-centroid, negligible low_band_energy, short. A crank adds a slow ratcheting transient train.",
     "Acoustically indistinguishable from DOORHdwr: identical brass and steel parts at identical scale. Both are narrowable at best; the filename decides which fixture.",
     "Against WNDWKnck: hardware is metal-on-metal with no pane resonance; a knock excites the glass, giving a ringing, tuned rattle."
    ],
    "confusable_with": [
     "DOORHdwr",
     "WNDWKnck",
     "WNDWMetl"
